title: Sample Book, Romantic Tapestries, 1986
medium: screen-printed and flocked on grasscloth, vinyl, paper
description:
A collection of 11 designs, each shown in multiple colorways. Printed on grasscloth and cork. The patterns include: "Potpourri", "Paco", "Valentina", "Elsinore", "Palm Drive", "Hana", "Kate", "Windswept", "LaLuna", "Sachet" and "Oui".

total of 93 pages of samples. pages 1-94 with page 2 missing. pages 32, 43, 58, 59, 61,63,64,85, and 87 each have 4 small samples per page.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Romantic Tapestries, 1986; Manufactured by Bob Mitchell Designs ; USA; screen-printed and flocked on grasscloth, vinyl, paper; 52 x 45.5 cm (20 1/2 x 17 15/16 in.); 1986-33-2-1/120
